Context: The George Brown College Foundation will be hosting the 10th annual Food Court Social on October 5, 2023, at the Waterfront Campus. Last year, the event raised over $500,000 for the George Brown College Augmented Education Program. This year's event includes food, drinks, and entertainment. Attendance is reserved exclusively for sponsors. For more information on becoming a sponsor or donating to the Silent Auction, visit the links "Become a Sponsor" and "Donate to Food Court Social". The contact person for inquiries is Samantha Walker, Events, Communications, & Administration Officer, who can be reached at 416-415-5000 ext. 3005 or Samantha.Walker@georgebrown.ca. The college's phone number is 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. For application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours and more, sign up on the website. The information in the text may be subject to change without notice.
